## Agent Behavior

After modifying files in `gitops/`:
- If an ArgoCD Application was changed, verify it uses `project: rhoai-demo`, has `manifest-generate-paths`, and has required labels (`app.kubernetes.io/part-of`, `demo.rhoai.io/step`)
- If a `kustomization.yaml` was changed, run `kustomize build <path>` to verify it renders without errors
- If resources were added or removed from a kustomization, verify the resource file exists and is listed
